  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372740/extras/d616cae3ee901858b6616cc1e38b4d1d.avif?t=1741717064\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372740/extras_big/d616cae3ee901858b6616cc1e38b4d1d.avif?t=1741717064 width=800 height=330 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Evil Timefall</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Evil Timefall - <strong>hardcore FPS</strong>, where you fight against <strong>medieval evil</strong>. Immerse yourself in <strong>dark horror</strong>, where you <strong>kill zombie knights, witches and demons</strong>. Dive into the bloody <strong>meat slaughter</strong>, where cruel enemies attack you from the darkness and wait for you around every corner. <strong>Upgrade your guns</strong> to execute more servants of the bloody lord of darkness.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Atmosphere</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game developers were inspired by the famous film <strong>\"<i>Army of Darkness</i>\"</strong>. The game recreates the <strong>atmosphere of horror and comedy</strong>. You will <strong>brutally destroy</strong> terrible monsters and <strong>smile</strong> at the sight of <strong>fountains of blood</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372740/extras/b5b163152c7b9f6cff52042741365a49.poster.avif?t=1741717064\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372740/extras/b5b163152c7b9f6cff52042741365a49.webm?t=1741717064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372740/extras/b5b163152c7b9f6cff52042741365a49.mp4?t=1741717064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is a <strong>classic retro shooter</strong> in which you <strong>kill crowds of aggressive enemies</strong>, pick up ammunition for your weapon and find first aid kits to restore health. Meet <strong>wizards</strong> at each level who will give you <strong>super power</strong> that improve your skills. Find chests with gold to <strong>improve and buy new types of weapons</strong>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >For whom is this game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>If you are a hardcore gamer who loves challenging shooters - this game is for you.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372740/extras/d616cae3ee901858b6616cc1e38b4d1d.avif?t=1741717064\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372740/extras_big/d616cae3ee901858b6616cc1e38b4d1d.avif?t=1741717064 width=800 height=330 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Evil Timefall</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Evil Timefall - <strong>hardcore FPS</strong>, where you fight against <strong>medieval evil</strong>. Immerse yourself in <strong>dark horror</strong>, where you <strong>kill zombie knights, witches and demons</strong>. Dive into the bloody <strong>meat slaughter</strong>, where cruel enemies attack you from the darkness and wait for you around every corner. <strong>Upgrade your guns</strong> to execute more servants of the bloody lord of darkness.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Atmosphere</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game developers were inspired by the famous film <strong>\"<i>Army of Darkness</i>\"</strong>. The game recreates the <strong>atmosphere of horror and comedy</strong>. You will <strong>brutally destroy</strong> terrible monsters and <strong>smile</strong> at the sight of <strong>fountains of blood</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372740/extras/b5b163152c7b9f6cff52042741365a49.poster.avif?t=1741717064\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372740/extras/b5b163152c7b9f6cff52042741365a49.webm?t=1741717064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372740/extras/b5b163152c7b9f6cff52042741365a49.mp4?t=1741717064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is a <strong>classic retro shooter</strong> in which you <strong>kill crowds of aggressive enemies</strong>, pick up ammunition for your weapon and find first aid kits to restore health. Meet <strong>wizards</strong> at each level who will give you <strong>super power</strong> that improve your skills. Find chests with gold to <strong>improve and buy new types of weapons</strong>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >For whom is this game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>If you are a hardcore gamer who loves challenging shooters - this game is for you.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
